":5,"tier":"archive","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Other Selected Research"]},{"id":"2606.26640","canonical_id":"2606.26640","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Cm-wavelength Studies of Molecular Gas and Star Formation at High Redshift with the SKA","authors":["Ran Wang","Jeff Wagg","Mark T. Sargent","Manuel Aravena","Mamta Pandey-Pommier","Elisabete da Cunha","Eric Murphy","Dominik Riechers","Jacqueline Hodge"],"categories":["astro-ph.GA"],"summary":"本文强调了SKA在高频段（>15 GHz）观测高红移星系低阶分子谱线的重要性，特别是研究早期宇宙年轻星系中的冷分子气体含量和活跃恒星形成区域。","date":"2026-06-26","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.26640","score":88,"stars":5,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"high-z galaxy gas","points":20}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Multi-phase and Molecular Gas","Galaxy Evolution"]},{"id":"2606.31583","canonical_id":"2606.31583","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Predisposition of galaxy clusters to producing exotic hyperbolic umbilic lensing configurations","authors":["Quentin Basto","Johan Richard","David J. Lagattuta","Ashish K. Meena","Harald Ebeling"],"categories":["astro-ph.CO"],"summary":"本文研究了双曲脐点(HU)奇特强引力透镜系统，通过参数化星系团质量模型在源平面绘制HU奇特像形成区域，并定义奇特共动体积(V_z<10)。在验证方法后应用于74个星系团模型，发现椭圆度与爱因斯坦半径或尖度组合最能区分高V_z系统，并估计每个星系团平均贡献约0.125个星系至其奇特体积，观测19个星系团有90%概率探测到至少一个HU系统。","date":"2026-07-01","url":"https://arxiv.org/abs/2606.31583","score":85,"stars":4,"tier":"recommended","mandatory":false,"score_breakdown":[{"label":"strong gravitational lensing","points":55},{"label":"pure cosmology","points":-30}],"must_read_reason":"","topics":["Strong Gravitational Lensing"]},{"id":"2606.31312","canonical_id":"2606.31312","version_count":1,"previous_versions":[],"title":"Dissecting the Obscured Core of GN20: an Active Galactic Nucleus Outshone by Young Stars","authors":["M. Hamed","L. Colina","P. G. Pérez-González","J. Álvarez Márquez","A. Crespo Gómez","L. A. Boogaard","A. Bik","H. Übler","S. E. I. Bosman","A. A